01:21:29,800 --> 01:21:32,800
指出了聖盃的位置
that pinpoints the exact location of the Grail.

884
01:21:32,880 --> 01:21:35,640
聖盃即將落入我們手
As you can see, the Grail is all but in our hands.

885
01:21:35,720 --> 01:21:36,930
但沒有你的許可
However, Your Highness,

886
01:21:37,010 --> 01:21:39,930
