we would not think of crossing your soil without your permission,

887
01:21:40,020 --> 01:21:45,160
也無法帶著聖盃離開你的邊界
nor of removing the Grail from your borders without suitable compensation.

888
01:21:47,730 --> 01:21:49,940
你們帶了什麼東西來？
What have you brought?

889
01:21:57,580 --> 01:22:00,120
全是一些很珍貴的東西  殿下
Precious valuables, Your Highness,

890
01:22:00,200 --> 01:22:04,410
這都是德國有錢的家族捐出來的東西
donated by some of the finest families in all of Germany.

891
01:22:09,590 --> 01:22:12,380
勞斯萊斯幽靈二型
Rolls-Royce Phantom Two.

892
01:22:12,460 --> 01:22:16,590
4.3公升  30匹馬力  6汽缸引擎
Four-point-three liter, 30 horsepower, six-cylinder engine,

893
01:22:16,680 --> 01:22:19,470
配備史洛姆伯格公司製造的下拖式化油器
