there's no silver medal for finishing second.

912
01:23:50,600 --> 01:23:53,060
你想喝點水嗎  馬庫斯？
Care to wet your whistle, Marcus?

913
01:23:53,150 --> 01:23:55,020
我寧願往你臉上吐口水
I'd rather spit in your face.

914
01:23:55,110 --> 01:23:57,610
但我並沒有那麼做...
But as I haven't got any spit...

915
01:23:59,990 --> 01:24:02,870
聖盃就在三到四里的範圍內
Must be within three or four miles.

916
01:24:02,950 --> 01:24:05,540
不然的話  就是我們走錯路了
Otherwise we are off the map.

917
01:24:07,040 --> 01:24:10,670
馬庫斯  我們就快要找到
Well, Marcus, we are on the brink of the recovery of

918
01:24:10,750 --> 01:24:14,380
人類史上最偉大的聖物
the greatest artifact in the history of mankind.

919
01:24:14,460 --> 01:24:18,260
你們是不自量力  在幫自己找麻煩
You're meddling with powers you cannot possibly comprehend.

920
