Dad, we're well out of range.

926
01:24:57,300 --> 01:24:58,460
那是我大舅子的車
That car belonged to my brother-in-law.

927
01:24:58,550 --> 01:25:00,090
快來吧
Come on, come on!

928
01:25:00,220 --> 01:25:02,430
