I can't see anyone up there.

929
01:25:02,510 --> 01:25:03,760
可能不是瓊斯吧
Maybe it wasn't even Jones.

930
01:25:03,840 --> 01:25:06,100
不  一定是他
No, it is him, all right.

931
01:25:06,180 --> 01:25:07,810
他就在附近
He's here somewhere.

932
01:25:08,850 --> 01:25:10,810
