- What?     - But don't you see?

980
01:33:36,440 --> 01:33:40,090
筆比槍還有力
The pen is mightier than the sword.

981
01:34:02,220 --> 01:34:03,630
看看你做的好事
Look what you did.

982
01:34:03,720 --> 01:34:05,220
這是戰爭
It's war.

983
01:34:11,020 --> 01:34:14,060
我不是告訴過你我們是來救你的嗎？
Didn't I tell you it was a rescue?

984
