- 爸  - 嗯？
- Dad!    - Yeah?

985
01:35:20,630 --> 01:35:22,130
這就是考古學研究？
You call this archeology?

986
01:35:22,210 --> 01:35:23,880
快離開這兒
Get out of there, Dad.

987
01:35:34,680 --> 01:35:36,390
我要怎麼下去？
How does one get off this thing?

988
01:35:43,320 --> 01:35:44,440
馬庫斯在哪堙H
Where's Marcus?

989
01:35:49,110 --> 01:35:50,700
爸
Dad!

990
01:35:54,120 --> 01:35:55,290
抓緊了  爸
Hang on, Dad!

991
01:36:02,170 --> 01:36:04,810
印第的爹  快把手伸過來
Father of Indy, give me your hand!

992
01:36:05,000 --> 01:36:06,090
薩拉
Sallah!

993
