我還以為我失去你了  兒子
I thought I'd lost you, boy!

1003
01:38:12,800 --> 01:38:14,970
我也是那麼想  爸
I thought you had too, sir.

1004
01:38:27,980 --> 01:38:29,520
那麼...
Well...

1005
01:38:31,780 --> 01:38:34,820
做得好  快走吧
Well done. Come on.

1006
01:38:37,870 --> 01:38:39,660
我們得出發了
Let's go, then.

1007
01:38:42,160 --> 01:38:45,120
你幹嘛還坐在那堨薿均H我們就快到了
Why are you sitting there resting when we're so near the end?

1008
01:38:45,210 --> 01:38:47,170
來吧
Come on, let's go!

1009
