我要的是長生不老  他的願望真的太渺小了
I'm going to be drinking my own health when he's gone the way of the dodo.

1026
01:42:55,210 --> 01:42:57,460
聖盃是我的
The Grail is mine,

1027
01:42:57,540 --> 01:42:59,500
你得幫我找到它
