1028
01:42:59,590 --> 01:43:01,590
開槍殺了我  對你一點好處都沒有
Shooting me won't get you anywhere.

1029
01:43:02,050 --> 01:43:03,800
你知道嗎？
You know something, Dr. Jones?

1030
01:43:03,880 --> 01:43:05,800
你說的對
You're absolutely right.

1031
01:43:08,470 --> 01:43:11,930
爸
Dad?

1032
